32
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:32,620
Take a coin.

33
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:34,860
You and I each pick one side.

34
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,660
Drop the coin vertically into the water.

35
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:38,980
The person whose side faces up

36
00:02:39,140 --> 00:02:40,140
when the coin falls
to the bottom will win.

37
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,500
That’s fair.

38
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:46,860
Step aside.

39
00:02:53,540 --> 00:02:56,540
May I ask this is...

40
00:02:58,020 --> 00:02:59,740
Master of Longzhu Gang, Long Aoyi.

41
00:02:59,860 --> 00:03:01,900
Right now I am the
personal maid of Master Li.

42
00:03:01,980 --> 00:03:03,300
My job is sweeping the floor.

43
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:04,500
Sorry for making you laugh.

44
00:03:05,380 --> 00:03:07,180
Interesting.

45
00:03:07,780 --> 00:03:09,740
They have a study partner.

46
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:11,940
Master Li has a gambling partner.

47
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:13,260
That’s all right.

48
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:15,740
Pick your side and make a bet.

49
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:30,220
There are no rules for
this kind of gamble.

50
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:31,380
You can’t cheat either.

51
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:32,620
How much do you want to bet?

52
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:35,220
I don’t need you here. Go back.

53
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:39,460
Gamble without me,
do you have confidence to win?

54
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:41,740
Do you?

55
00:03:44,580 --> 00:03:45,860
Make the biggest bet

56
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:47,260
you can afford

57
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:48,580
to scare Mr. Shen away.

58
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:50,580
