59
00:03:50,580 --> 00:03:51,820
without actual winning or losing.

60
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:56,580
Let’s be decisive.

61
00:03:57,900 --> 00:03:58,340
How much?

62
00:03:58,620 --> 00:03:59,260
The biggest.

63
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:07,260
To show my sincerity,

64
00:04:07,940 --> 00:04:09,740
I’ll bet the deed of my Silk Manor.

65
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:11,530
Well...

66
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:13,220
Yan Bin.

67
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:13,810
The deed?

68
