00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:32,900
Mr. Shen.

94
00:05:33,260 --> 00:05:34,380
You mustn’t do that.

95
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:37,220
This old man can’t take

96
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:39,540
such a fierce bet from Li Qingliu.

97
00:05:39,780 --> 00:05:40,980
