104
00:05:57,980 --> 00:05:58,660
We bet on the head side.

105
00:05:59,060 --> 00:06:00,060
Place your bet.

106
00:06:00,060 --> 00:06:01,460
Sir, you can drop the coin anytime.

107
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:35,620
Stop!

108
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:44,700
You have shown me

109
00:06:45,020 --> 00:06:46,260
