he puts all his efforts on this.

214
00:10:23,940 --> 00:10:26,540
Chubby. Stop chatting, come to work.

215
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:28,420
Hurry up.

216
00:10:29,180 --> 00:10:29,820
Coming.

217
00:10:48,380 --> 00:10:49,060
Master.

218
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:52,900
