but I have to admit

225
00:11:03,660 --> 00:11:05,460
he is something in business.

226
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:07,500
Perhaps we should learn from him

227
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:08,900
about how to make money.

228
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:10,860
