fifty-three thousand taels.

230
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:13,980
Master.

231
00:11:14,020 --> 00:11:15,420
Aren’t we

232
00:11:15,660 --> 00:11:17,140
looting a burning house?

233
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:18,580
